                  <Text layoutX="211.0" layoutY="438.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Fig. 1 Showing Simple Diagram of a Computer System" textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
