                        <Font name="Segoe UI" size="16.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Text>
                  <Text layoutX="103.0" layoutY="1327.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="* The CPU processes it in a word processor (Process)." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="Segoe UI" size="16.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Text>
                  <Text layoutX="103.0" layoutY="1348.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="* It shows on the screen (Output)." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="Segoe UI" size="16.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Text>
                  <Text layoutX="103.0" layoutY="1369.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="* You save it to the hard drive (Storage)." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
